title: NBA, Raptors, Warriors, Steph Curry, and the Lakers
itunes:title: NBA, Raptors, Warriors, Steph Curry, and the Lakers
description:
Colin discusses the NBA Finals and explains that injuries were  the major factor. He believes the Golden State Warriors dynasty is over and G Steph Curry will need help. Colin also has more on New Orleans Pelicans F Anthony Davis, and where the NBA is most likely headed. Guests include Chris Broussard, Tom Tolbert, Ric Bucher, and Frank Caliendo.
